divs: Sighting Detailswhen reviewing the photograph I noticed the object under the Funnel cloud. When I snapped the shot it was of the signage located in Lafayette, Indiana on Creasy Lane east of SR 38 about 500 yards from a construction sites main drive on the west side of the Road. The Photograph is viewed from south to North. And I did not notice the Funnel cloud or the object at the time, my mind was on the signage. I question to you did the object drop from the Funnel Cloud? Did it cause the Cloud? just for your eyes.
